I don't understand your question. Are you asking why the 1+5 has face unlock? If so, then it is just another security option to unlock your phone. 
If you mis-typed and asked why it doesn't have face unlock then go to Settings\Security & lock screen\Smart lock to find it.

@amj 
If anyone else is as paranoid as you then all they have to do is go to Settings/Advanced and switch OFF the option 'Join user experience program'. 
It doesn't bother me because I have nothing to hide, but it certainly sounds as if you have.

@Vioo 
People keep complaining about the lack of a SD slot on this phone, so here are the facts. 
I ran Geekbench on my OP5 and it showed that the camera can take 5.69 pictures/sec, and the camera memory score was 26.9 pictures/sec. There isn't a mobile phone in existence using a SD card to store pictures that can work that fast. SD cards are a slow, antiquated, obsolete form of storage that is redundant on phones made today; and that is why manufacturers are no longer supporting them.

